NTP
=======

This module configures NTP.

You can optionnaly pass a "server_info" which is actually a string prepended to pool.ntp.org.
Ex: server_info = "fr" => fr.pool.ntp.org
This has effect only on Openntpd, whcih means only on Debian/Ubuntu systems, and not EC2 either.

